1. Hermes Agent — inspiration & integration

This dashboard is designed to observe and interoperate with Hermes Agent
by Nous Research (https://hermes-agent.nousresearch.com,
https://github.com/nousresearch/hermes-agent), distributed under MIT.

The dashboard's Hermes page mirrors elements of the Hermes Agent
visual identity (deep teal background, cream text, pixel-mark amber
halo, Pantheon persona vocabulary). Those design tokens and naming
conventions belong to Nous Research and are used here to render an
operator surface for the agent on the user's own machine. No Hermes
Agent code is bundled.

